&lt;p>Hello, I&amp;rsquo;m Halil Arda Özongun, a passionate Computer Science student at Bilkent University with a minor in Mathematics. My interests are deep learning, competitive programming and the mathematics underneath. I am currently working under &lt;a href="https://www.cs.bilkent.edu.tr/~adundar/" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Asst. Prof. Ayşegül Dündar&lt;/a> in the &lt;a href="https://dlr.bilkent.edu.tr/" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DLR Lab&lt;/a> on single-stage diffusion models and &lt;a href="https://web.cs.hacettepe.edu.tr/~erkut/" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Erkut Erdem&lt;/a> on improving image quality in low light using deep learning algorithms.&lt;/p>
